A [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].

This pool aims to provide a simple reward sharing scheme and fast payments.

The service was first available for beta testing starting February 26, 2011 (1.1).

##Reward distribution

* Proportional: 3% fee.
* Pay-Per-Share mode: Current rate shown on website.

